## Desktop Notifications (Optional)

If using `notify-send` for notifications, customize styling in `~/.config/dunst/dunstrc`:

```ini
[{{COMPONENT_NAME}}-notifications]
    summary = "{{COMPONENT_NAME}}*"
    frame_color = "#FFA500"
    background = "#1a1000"
    foreground = "#ffffff"
    timeout = 3
```

Reload: `killall dunst && dunst &`

